			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1) Open debugbook&#xD;&#xA;2) Got to Region&#xD;&#xA;3) Act 3&#xD;&#xA;4) Wyrm's Crossing&#xD;&#xA;5) Bridge Checkpoint&#xD;&#xA;6.0) oe OIStartOrinJournalist to start the dialog (do the other steps below first if you want them enabled)&#xD;&#xA;6.1) oe OIEnableOrinJournalist to enable journal as Orin&#xD;&#xA;6.2) oe OIMetOrinOnce to enable that you've met Orin in previous impersonation." />
			<attribute id="autoFidelity" type="LSString" value="Silver" />
